# Start/Stop & Health
- Start both (preferred): `npm run dev:safe`.
- If unavailable:
  - Baseline: `npm run build && npm run start`  (port 3000)
  - Sandbox: `PORT=3001 NEXT_DISABLE_TURBOPACK=1 npm run dev`
- Verify after start:
  - `npm run agent:status` must return ok:true (200 on 3000, 3001, and /manifest.webmanifest).
  - `npm run health:check` must return ok:true (200 on /api/healthz for both).
  - `npm run console:check:sandbox` must return ok:true (no console errors).